        <content type="html"><![CDATA[<p>小程序中有相对路径和绝对路径的区别</p><p><img src="https://raw.githubusercontent.com/ssuiw97/PicForHexo/master/MiniProgram/ReadingNotes/mp3-1.jpg" alt="加入图片后的文件结构"></p><h1 id="绝对路径"><a href="#绝对路径" class="headerlink" title="绝对路径"></a>绝对路径</h1><figure class="highlight html"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">image</span> <span class="attr">src</span>=<span class="string">"/images/avatar/avatar-1.png"</span> /&gt;</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><ul><li>以“/”开头，“/”代表根目录</li></ul><h1 id="相对路径"><a href="#相对路径" class="headerlink" title="相对路径"></a>相对路径</h1><figure class="highlight html"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">image</span> <span class="attr">src</span>=<span class="string">"../../images/avatar/avatar-1.png"</span> /&gt;</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><ul><li>“..”代表向上一级</li></ul><blockquote><p>这里使用绝对路径更加简洁</p></blockquote>]]></content>
      
      
